snippet.title: AQUAMAN (2018) | Behind the Scenes of Jason Momoa DC Movie
snippet.description:
Making of Aquaman
Subscribe and click the notification bell HERE: http://goo.gl/SrrTlT
Check out our new "Chill Out/Relax" Music Channel:  http://bit.ly/BestRelaxingMusic
#Aquaman #BehindTheScenes.

Plot:
Arthur Curry learns that he is the heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, and must step forward to lead his people and be a hero to the world.

Genre: Action, Sci-Fi, Fantasy
Director: James Wan
Cast: Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe, Patrick Wilson, Nicole Kidman, Dolph Lundgren, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II
Production & Credits: DC Comics,DC Entertainment,Panoramic Pictures
Distributors: Warner Bros.
Country: USA, Australia

Some of the best and most funniest movie moments happen behind the scenes.  #FilmIsNowExtra & Movie Bloopers channel gives you the latest and best behind the scenes footage, gag reel, vfx breakdown, interviews, featurettes and deleted/alternate scenes. We give you the before, during and after that goes into making movies.
